Class TLFDataSink

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gradoop.flink.io.impl.tlf.TLFDataSink
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataSink

    public class TLFDataSink
extends Object
implements DataSink
    Writes an EPGM representation into one TLF file. The format is documented at TLFFileFormat.
